ds/2025/01/jools_hootenanny_2025-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jools_hootenanny_2025-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jools_hootenanny_2025-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jade-thirlwall">JADE</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cmat">CMAT</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jungle">Jungle</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-boomtown-rats">The Boomtown Rats</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/queen">Queen</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/roger-taylor">Roger Taylor</a>和 Sister Sledge 的 Kathy Sledge 都是今年在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jools-holland">Jools Holland</a>的 Hootenanny 中表演的明星。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="799" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cmat-interview-ireland-new-music-ivors-album-3759488"><b>CMAT：“爱尔兰人一直都很出色——但也有很多创伤”</b></a></li></ul><p>自 1994 年以来，一年一度的 BBC 节目已成为一项传统，主持人会邀请古今众多的音乐明星来敲响新年的钟声。整个节目可通过 BBC iPlayer <a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/iplayer/episode/m0026dy8/jools-annual-hootenanny-202425" target="_blank" rel="noopener">观看</a>。</p><p> 2024/2025 年版的杰出表演者包括前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/little-mix">Little Mix</a>歌手 JADE，她演奏了她 2024 年的单曲“Fantasy”，以及唐娜·萨默 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/donna-summer">Donna Summer</a> ) 的“Hot Stuff”和埃迪·弗洛伊德 (Eddie Floyd) 的“Knock On Wood”的混合曲。由 Jools Holland 和他的节奏布鲁斯管弦乐团演奏。她的搭档<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jordan-stephens">乔丹·斯蒂芬斯</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rizzle-kicks">（Rizzle Kicks</a>的前成员）也在场，随着女友的表演热情地跳舞——请看下面。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="JADE - Hot Stuff / Knock On Wood（Jools&#39; Annual Hootenanny 2024）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/rfMhZc4kkus?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>可以说，最抢镜的表演来自爱尔兰创作型歌手 CMAT，他演奏了俏皮版本的“Have Fun！”收录于她 2023 年专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/cmat-crazymad-for-me-review-lyrics-tracklist-3512398">Crazymad, For Me</a> 》中，随后以<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mariah-carey">玛丽亚·凯莉 (Mariah Carey)</a>于 1994 年录制的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/harry-nilsson">哈利·尼尔森 (Harry Nilsson)</a>歌曲《Without You》史诗般的演绎结束了演出。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="CMAT - 没有你（Jools 年度 Hootenanny 2024）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/G0DTzK8eDdk?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>伦敦新灵魂/舞蹈团体 Jungle 还演奏了他们 2024 年的单曲《Let&#39;s Go Back》，以及 2023 年的《Back On 74》和 2014 年的《Busy Earnin》，而加拿大蓝草乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-dead-south">The Dead South</a>表演了《A Little Devil/20》英里跳跃&#39;。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="丛林 - 让我们回去吧（Jools 年度 Hootenanny 2024）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/evBptwEuEPo?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="死亡南方 - 小恶魔 / 20 英里跳跃（Jools 年度 Hootenanny 2024）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-Io6OOd25nU?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在老牌表演方面，Kathy Sledge 演唱了 Sister Sledge 的经典歌曲《We Are Family》和《Thinking Of You》，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bob-geldof">Bob Geldof</a>的 Boomtown Rats 则演唱了他们 70 年代末的第一单曲《Rat Trap》和《I Don》就像星期一一样。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="凯西·斯莱奇 - 我们是一家人（Jools&#39; Annual Hootenanny 2024）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/REwh42HI5dY?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="The Boomtown Rats - Rat Trap（Jools 年度 Hootenanny 2024）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/r0pw_VC-3LA?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/marc-almond">Marc Almond</a>演奏了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/soft-cell">Soft Cell</a>的《Say Hello, Wave Goodbye》版本，而 Queen 鼓手 Roger Taylor 则演唱了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/little-richard">Little Richard</a>歌曲的混合曲《Keep-A-Knockin》和《Tutti Frutti》，以及一首二重唱与歌手路易丝·马歇尔合作的《压力之下》。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="马克·阿尔蒙德 (Marc Almond) - 说你好，挥手告别（Jools 年度 Hootenanny 2024）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/__jn5_v8qqE?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="罗杰·泰勒 - 在压